class=\"kv-control-placeholder kv-_section\"\n    data-kv-control=\"background\">\n  <\/div> <div class='kv-background  ' style=\" background-color: rgb(237,241,247);\">\n        \n        <div class='kv-background-inner '  style=\"\n          \n          \n          \n          background-color: rgb(237,241,247);\n          \"><\/div>\n          \n<\/div>\n  <div class=\"position-relative kv-content\">\n    <div\n    class=\"kv-control-placeholder kv-_section\"\n    data-kv-control=\"content\">\n  <\/div> <div class=\"kv-ee-section kv-ee-section--lg\"><div class=\"kv-ee-container\"><div class=\"kv-ee-row\"><div class=\"kv-ee-col-lg-10 kv-ee-offset-lg-1 kv-ee-align-left kv-notify-inview kv-ee-section-text\">  <h2 class=\"kv-ee-section-title kv-ee-section-title--md\" data-type=\"text\" tabindex=\"0\">Acupuncture weight loss treatment\u9488\u7078\u51cf\u80a5<span data-prop=\"title\" class=\"ck-editable-element\" data-editable=\"basic\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/span><\/h2> <p class=\"kv-ee-description\" data-type=\"text\" tabindex=\"0\">Acupuncture helps with losing weight;<br><br>\nThe mechanism of acupuncture weight loss is mainly to:\nImprove the metabolism;\nAdjust the digestive function;\nAdjust endocrine function;<br><br>Acupuncture treatment can promote metabolism, increase energy consumption, promote the\nmobilization of body fat and fat decomposition, and achieve its weight loss effect.<br><br>Acupuncture treatment can inhibit the hyperinfluous appetite of obese patients, reduce the\namount of food, and inhibit the gastrointestinal digestion and absorption function of the\npatient&amp;#39;s hyperactivity, reduce the absorption of energy by the body, thereby reducing energy\nintake<br><br>After acupuncture, it can inhibit the peristalsis of the gastrointestinal tract and inhibit the\nsecretion of gastric acid, thereby reducing hunger and achieving the purpose of acupuncture\nweight loss.<br><br>Acupuncture helps the hormonal balance. The acupuncture treatment adjusts the function of\nthe systems of the hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal cortex and sympathetic-adrenal medullary,\nwhich we consider as the \u201cmaster switch\u201d for our body shape, so it helps with our weight loss\nprocess;<br><br>Acupuncture also helps reduce stress, so the regulated treatment can eliminate stress eating\nand prevent extra food intake.<br><br><b>Why does acupuncture weight loss treatment work so well?<br><\/b><br>After collecting your personal health history and diagnosis, Dr. Amber develops an individualized, customized treatment plan tailored to you and your specific concerns and goals. <br>\n\n<br>Acupuncture weight loss treatment is a green healthy method; there is no drug use, no strict food intake restriction, only the method of external treatment and reasonable lifestyle changes, help you gradually become slim without pain. <br><br>The more important one is, that acupuncture is not only to lose weight but more importantly, to lose dimensions and mainly to lose fat, not muscle, to help build up our body shape.<b><br><\/b><br><br><b>Whom is the ideal candidate for the acupuncture weight loss treatment<br><\/b>acupuncture weight loss treatment works effectively on people around 20 to 50 years old. <br>\n\n<br>The human body is mature enough and has functional properties at this age. Women during postpartum, and menopause. All of these periods are very intense endocrine changes. In the process of acupuncture weight loss treatment, many women with symptoms such as menstrual irregularities and amenorrhea do not treat these symptoms in the process of weight loss, but often through acupuncture, the original symptoms can be improved, which is the result of improved endocrine.<br> \n\n<br>Acupuncture weight loss treatment is effective for hypertension, diabetes, hyperlipidemia, fatty liver, obesity etc, not only helping with weight loss but also helping with other symptoms. <br>\n\n<br>However, acupuncture weight loss treatment is not recommended for people with certain diseases (complicated tumours, blood, cardiovascular and cerebrovascular diseases), and people in special periods (pregnant women, lactating women, etc.)<br><b><br>Is there any side effect during the process of treatment?<br><\/b>Most people won&#8217;t have any discomfort feeling, except: Better with sleep, less stress, and for women, the period becomes more regular and less PMS because the treatment helps with internal hormonal balance and reduces the stress;\n\nFor some people, lack of appetite, thirst, and increased frequency of bowel movements may occur during the treatment process, especially at the beginning of the treatment. <br><br>Because the internal functions of the body are constantly adjusted, which accelerates the metabolism and continuously consumes energy, some clinical symptoms appear. When the body regains its balance, these symptoms disappear. &nbsp;<br><span data-prop=\"description\" class=\"ck-editable-element\" data-editable=\"basic\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/span><\/p>  <\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n<style scoped>.hagopy24 .kv-ee-section-title{color:var(--kv-ee-title1)}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-description{line-height:1.75}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-overline{color:var(--kv-ee-text2);letter-spacing:.02em;margin-bottom:.25rem !important;margin-top:0 !important}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-left{text-align:left}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-center{text-align:center}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-center .kv-ee-section-subtitle,.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-center .kv-ee-section-title,.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-center .kv-ee-section-description{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-right{text-align:right}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-right .kv-ee-section-subtitle,.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-right .kv-ee-section-title,.hagopy24 .kv-ee-align-right .kv-ee-section-description{margin-left:auto}.hagopy24 .kv-ee-button{margin-right:1rem}<\/style><div\n      class=\"kv-control-placeholder kv-_page\"\n      data-kv-control=\"3\">\n    <\/div> <s